data.title: PJ Masks Party Bag Label Pack
data.meta_description: Our PJ Masks party bag label pack is perfect for adding a child's favourite PJ Heroes to a themed party. Personalised and non-personalised available.
data.text:
Our PJ Masks party bag label pack is perfect for adding a child’s favourite PJ Heroes to a PJ Masks themed party. Option 1 features Catboy, Owlette and Gekko dynamically posing with the text “Thanks for coming to my party!”. Option 2 is personalised and features the masks and logo with the text “Thanks for coming to ___’s party!” In each pack, you receive eight labels.

This PJ Masks party bag label pack is part of our birthday parties collection – click here to view more of our birthday party category.

About Stickerscapes Birthday Party Collection

Our birthday party collection is perfect for adding a finishing touch or creating a theme for any party. Featuring Peppa Pig, My Little Pony, Transformers and more, our window stickers and labels are easy to apply and great for adding fun and unique decorations to any themed birthday party.

If you have any questions about our designs or application, please feel free to contact our friendly customer service team.
